Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.94,中文,,0,0,0,,做的不錯 帕特希亞\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well done, Patricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.82,中文,,0,0,0,,蕩婦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Slut!
