Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:38.54,中文,,0,0,0,,看著對方的眼睛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Look each other in the eye, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.25,中文,,0,0,0,,然後觸碰\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}...touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.04,中文,,0,0,0,,絕對是她最可怕的噩夢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Literally her worst nightmare.
