Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.34,中文,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.98,中文,,0,0,0,,-和我說說 -沒什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Talk to me. - It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.06,中文,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我感覺不到我的腳了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I can't feel my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.50,中文,,0,0,0,,你還記得我們曾經玩「從頭到腳」嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you remember we used to go top-to-toe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.60,中文,,0,0,0,,現在的孩子都很怪\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Now kids are so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.12,中文,,0,0,0,,-我們以前總是玩那個遊戲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- We used to do that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.62,中文,,0,0,0,,-對呀 我們那時才十歲 也很可愛\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Yeah, when we were ten and cute.
