Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.96,中文,,0,0,0,,就是別說了 行嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Just don't, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:32.96,中文,,0,0,0,,別偷我的東西了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Stop stealing my things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是試試它好不好使\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm just checking it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.94,中文,,0,0,0,,哦 它絕對好使\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Oh, it's working, it's definitely working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.76,中文,,0,0,0,,噓\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}'Shh!'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.18,中文,,0,0,0,,玩的開心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.62,中文,,0,0,0,,這真是個十分體貼的禮物 謝謝你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It's actually a really thoughtful present. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.58,中文,,0,0,0,,馬丁給我了那個小雕塑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}And Martin getting me that sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:05.42,中文,,0,0,0,,他為了買到這個東西肯定花了不少心血\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He must have bent over backwards to get something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我覺得自己好幸運\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I feel very lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:15.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟你說啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I have to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.14,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:25.26,中文,,0,0,0,,那個雕像是我從別人的工作室順手拿的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I stole that sculpture from a certain somebody's studio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.30,中文,,0,0,0,,然後想通過馬丁找個買主\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and then I tried to sell it through Martin,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不過馬丁把雕像留下了 還送給了你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}but Martin took it and gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:31.97,中文,,0,0,0,,這事你可別當著老爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Just don't put it pride of place when Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.01,中文,,0,0,0,,呃 當著他們的面說\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}well, when they come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:36.44,中文,,0,0,0,,-好嗎 因為 -好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- OK? Because... - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:44.38,中文,,0,0,0,,克萊爾\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Claire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.26,中文,,0,0,0,,-克萊爾 -噓 快睡吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Claire! - Shh. Go to sleep.
