Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我們越快適應 就能越快離開這裏\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}The sooner we get on with it, the sooner we are out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.97,中文,,0,0,0,,-這外套真好看 -謝啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- That's a really nice outfit. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:31.26,中文,,0,0,0,,深入挖掘你的回憶\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Delve into your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:34.85,中文,,0,0,0,,想想你無法釋懷的東西\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Think of something you can't let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.85,中文,,0,0,0,,一段噪音\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}A moment of noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.98,中文,,0,0,0,,一個緊張時刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}A moment of tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.69,中文,,0,0,0,,-不要 -現在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Not for now. - Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:53.21,中文,,0,0,0,,想想你覺得內心平靜的時刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}...A moment when you were peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.75,中文,,0,0,0,,要是你能隨心所欲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}If you could change
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.58,中文,,0,0,0,,改變世上的任何東西 你想改變什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}anything in the whole world, what would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我的大腿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}My thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.66,中文,,0,0,0,,整個世界你就想改變這個\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}In the whole world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.78,中文,,0,0,0,,可別跟別人說 那你呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Don't tell anyone I said that. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:09.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直對自己的顏值挺不滿的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I've always been insecure about my face.
