Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.70,中文,,0,0,0,,-你不用不滿啊 -謝了 不過\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- You shouldn't. - Thank you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.50,中文,,0,0,0,,不啊 真的 你的鼻子一點問題都沒有\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, seriously, there's nothing wrong with your nose.
