Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.46,中文,,0,0,0,,-我的意思是 你的臉 -你說什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- I mean, there's nothing wrong... - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.81,中文,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:24.07,中文,,0,0,0,,-啊 -哦天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Ah! - Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我總說錯話\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I always say the wrong thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.14,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Ah! Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.38,中文,,0,0,0,,好燙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.42,中文,,0,0,0,,這是幹嘛 我在自己家都不幹這些活的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What is this? I don't even do this in my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.10,中文,,0,0,0,,道理很簡單\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Well, it's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我們是花錢給人家做掃除 還不能出聲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}We've paid them to let us clean their house in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.10,中文,,0,0,0,,老天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.46,中文,,0,0,0,,我不想像老師一樣批評你們\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I don't want to come down on you like a schoolteacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:12.14,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你們明目張膽違反這裏的規則\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}but I'm afraid your flagrant lack of respect for the one rule
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.50,中文,,0,0,0,,恐怕已經影響到其他學生了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}that we have here is now affecting the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,-顧客 -你是說囚犯嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Clients. - Inmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.22,中文,,0,0,0,,-或者說是清潔工吧 -參與者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Cleaners? - Participants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:22.18,中文,,0,0,0,,你們對這個活動有什麼不滿嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Do you have a problem with the programme?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:29.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我建議你們在這裏靜坐一小時\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I suggest you try sitting here in silence for the next hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.31,中文,,0,0,0,,對你們有好處的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}It will benefit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.54,中文,,0,0,0,,我以靈魂發誓 肯定有好處\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I swear by my soul, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.98,中文,,0,0,0,,我翻你的包來著\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I went through your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.77,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.30,中文,,0,0,0,,我什麼也沒找到 所以你得\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I couldn't find anything, so you're just going to have
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.19,中文,,0,0,0,,親自告訴我你到底怎麼了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}to tell me what's going on with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.10,中文,,0,0,0,,說話 不然我就喊啦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Talk! Or I will scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:12.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我獲得了升職到芬蘭的機會\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I got the Finland promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.20,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼升職到芬蘭\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What Finland promotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎麼還問 我都跟你說過了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}How can you ask that? I've told you about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 挺好的呀\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I know the Finland promotion, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.37,中文,,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.62,中文,,0,0,0,,這是不是就意味著你現在是土豪啦 抱大腿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Does that mean you're a millionaire now? Handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.06,中文,,0,0,0,,別傻了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.38,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊 會是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Yes, it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:28.22,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你有錢還不開心嗎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}All that money makes you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我準備拒絕掉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I'm turning it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.98,中文,,0,0,0,,什麼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.86,中文,,0,0,0,,為什麼 因為馬丁唄\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Why? Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.00,中文,,0,0,0,,馬丁說這樣對傑克不公平\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Martin says it would be unfair on Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.14,中文,,0,0,0,,傑克是她的繼子 他真是個怪胎\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Jake's her stepson, he's really weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.78,中文,,0,0,0,,從癥狀來看是這樣 但是沒人這麼說\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}probably clinically, but no-one really talks about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.30,中文,,0,0,0,,要是她有超過一天不在身邊 他就嚇尿了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He freaks out if she's gone for longer than a day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:49.34,中文,,0,0,0,,他甚至想跟她一起洗澡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}and he's got this thing about trying to get in the bath with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.86,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 傑克 不行\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}No, no. No, Jake. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:58.33,中文,,0,0,0,,他都十五歲了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}He's 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.29,中文,,0,0,0,,-他又不是你兒子 -重點不在這\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- He's not your son. - That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:04.68,中文,,0,0,0,,-去吧 -我就知道你會這麼說\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- Go! - I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.26,中文,,0,0,0,,-你不是一直想要這個機會嗎 -我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- This is what you've always wanted. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.93,中文,,0,0,0,,-再也不用穿職業裝 還到處都是雪 -我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- No more power suits, fuckload of snow. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.87,中文,,0,0,0,,那地方很適合你這種冷血動物啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Perfect place for your cold, cold heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:13.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道 但我做不到\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}I know, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.33,中文,,0,0,0,,-我有我的責任 -噢 別鬧了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}- I have responsibilities. - Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.06,中文,,0,0,0,,別讓別人妨礙你追求理想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Don't let other people get in the way of what you really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:22.66,中文,,0,0,0,,芬蘭就是你的理想\N{\3c&H000000&\fs35}Finland is what you really want.
